Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Army
    The Army class represents an army with variable amounts of foot soldiers, tanks, and planes.
    ArmySimulationFrame
    Class that acts as the JFrame for and controls a visual simulation
    ArmySimulationMain
    Class that controls both the command line simulation and visual simulation.
    Battle
    The Battle class represents a turn based battle between two armies using discretized versions of Lanchaster's equations.
    SimulationPanel
    The SimulationPanel class extends JPanel and is the interface used to run the simulation.
    UserInputPanel
    The UserInputPanel class extends JPanel and is the interface used to collect the information for both armies from the user.
